<br>
She was shaken from her deep concentration by something almost imperceptible ... a shimmer of freshness ... of green ... and a faint whisper of a voice ... Kalyndria's.  And then it faded away.<br>
<br>
Athene felt briefly mournful, but there had been something in that moment of passing clarity that spoke of light-hearted friendship ... and goodness, so Athene returned to her work, ... somehow refreshed.<br>
