<br>
Walking down the guildhall Kandiya kept thinking.  She remembered the first time she had met Kaly.  <br>
<br>
&quot;I thought she was insane!&quot;  Kandiya burst out and she stifled her tears and turned it into laughter.  Covering her mouth she thought to herself, &quot;They will think I am insane if I keep bursting out like that!&quot;<br>
